ShipConstructor + ShipBasicInfo + modulesAttached = a ship in the battleField
ShipConstructor recieves a Info = {
		many basic infos (ShipBasicInfo)...
		...
		...
		modules:ShipDesign.getModule() // (modulesAttached)
}



ShipDesigner:
parameter:
1.ship

interface:
getModules:
return attached modulesCode as an array

mode:
read-only (not in starstation)
read-write (in starstation)

read-only (only view the modules and the ship)
read-write ()